<HEADLINE>
<P>
DEEP SPRINGS COLLEGE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
As an alumnus of Deep Springs College, I want to commend Thomas J. Meyer and 
Max Aguilera-Hellweg for "School on the Range" (May 14). In both words and 
photographs, they allowed the place and people to speak for themselves, and 
kept to a minimum the stereotypic interpretations inevitable of "outsiders." 
</P>
<P>
JAMES D. MOREFIELD 
</P>
<P>
Claremont 
</P>
</TEXT>
