</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
It is true. A picture is worth a thousand words. The picture on the cover of 
Charles Manson brought forth many words for me: insensitivity, cruelty, 
manipulation, powerlessness, barbarity, persecution -- the list goes on. What a 
way to start Mother's Day. 
</P>
<P>
ELAINE PARKER 
</P>
<P>
Del Mar 
</P>
