<HEADLINE>
<P>
THE COCAINE WAR 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I wonder why our government doesn't force Colombia to get in the fight against 
drugs. Why not start with a boycott of Colombian coffee, probably their second 
most important and profitable export, other than cocaine? You can't kill an 
octopus by cutting off its tentacles -- you've got to go to its heart. 
</P>
<P>
BOB RAMSAY 
</P>
<P>
