<HEADLINE>
<P>
BOARD VOTE ON THE AIDS ORDINANCE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Is anyone paying attention out there? You people who continue to support County 
Supervisors Gaddi H. Vasquez, Don R. Roth and Roger R. Stanton. You people who 
continue to re-elect Rep. William E. Dannemeyer who stands before groups, opens 
his mouth and spews out falsehoods which only further ignite the hysteria, hate 
and ignorance of the uneducated and short-sighted opposition to an anti-AIDS 
discrimination ordinance. 
</P>
<P>
Thanks to these officials, Orange County can now hold its head in shame as 
being the only urban county in California to ban this ordinance. How long are 
you going to keep your heads in the sand and pretend this is a "gay disease" 
which we can ignore? 
</P>
