Ignorance and fear cannot be tolerated in the fight against AIDS. Don't wait 
until you are personally affected by AIDS-related death of a friend or 
co-worker. Let Vasquez, Roth, Stanton and particularly Dannemeyer know they 
made a major error and that you won't continue to support such backward 
thinking. 
