HAWTHORNE TRASH PICKUP 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Hawthorne residential trash customers whose normal service day would be 
Tuesday, July 4, will have their trash picked up Monday, July 3, due to the 
observance of the Independence Day holiday. Governmental and private dumping 
sites will be closed July 4. 
</P>
