<SUBJECT>
<P>
HARVEY, JERRY; Z CHANNEL; SPORTSCHANNEL AMERICA; TELEVISION PROGRAMMING; 
TELEVISION NETWORKS; MOTION PICTURES; ACQUISITIONS; CABLE TELEVISION; PAY 
TELEVISION 
</P>
