SQUARE; CHINA -- REVOLTS; CHINA -- ARMED FORCES; CHINA -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; 
CHINA -- ECONOMY; DEMONSTRATIONS -- CHINA; DISSIDENTS -- CHINA; STUDENTS; 
DEMOCRACY; GOVERNMENT REFORM 
</P>
