FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
In some Friday editions, a headline incorrectly stated that the desert tortoise 
had been added to the state's endangered species list. In fact, the tortoise is 
now considered a threatened species, a less serious designation. 
</P>
</TEXT>
